It's all in your
imagination, I promise.

01:05.633 --> 01:07.833
There are no ghosts
in this house.

01:07.835 --> 01:09.368
There's no monster under the bed

01:09.370 --> 01:13.605
and there's definitely no
bad man in your cupboard.

01:15.276 --> 01:17.910
Now, come on, go back to sleep.

01:31.859 --> 01:35.494
Look, let's talk about
this in the morning.

03:06.487 --> 03:08.787
- Look, it's been going
on for three nights, now.

03:08.789 --> 03:10.022
It has to stop.

03:10.024 --> 03:11.456
- Will you give her a break?

03:11.458 --> 03:15.294
It's just gonna take her a
while to settle in, that's all.

03:15.296 --> 03:17.262
- Right, so in the
meantime I just keep goin'

03:17.264 --> 03:19.932
